snippet.title: The Backrooms: Descent Trailer
snippet.description:
The Backrooms: Descent
available on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2728250/The_Backrooms_Descent/

The Backrooms: Descent is a 1-4 player co-op horror experience. You are tasked with descending into the vast levels of the Backrooms which have dangerous entities while also finding evidence of previous research teams before you find your escape.
